languages.text: "Лорд-капитан, служители священного культа множество вахт смиренно ожидали встречи с вами. Желаете ли вы принять их, или им следует удалиться и более не надеяться на аудиенцию?"

"Lord Captain, the cult representatives have waited patiently for many watches to have an audience with you. Will you receive them, or do you wish to send them on their way without granting their request?"
languages.original_text: "Лорд-капитан, служители священного культа множество вахт смиренно ожидали встречи с вами. Желаете ли вы принять их, или им следует удалиться и более не надеяться на аудиенцию?"

traits.locale_text: "Lord Captain, members of a sacred cult have humbly waited for many cycles to meet you. Would you like to receive them, or are they to depart and relinquish their hope for an audience?"

languages.text: «Lord Capitán, los representantes del culto llevan muchas guardias esperando pacientemente una audiencia con usted. ¿Los recibirá o prefiere enviarlos de vuelta sin atender a su solicitud?».
languages.original_text: "Lord Captain, the cult representatives have waited patiently for many watches to have an audience with you. Will you receive them, or do you wish to send them on their way without granting their request?"

languages.text: “舰长大人，教派的众多代表已经耐心等待了几十巡，诚信希望能见您一面。您打算接待他们吗？还是说，您不打算答应他们的请求，希望打发他们回去？”
languages.original_text: "Lord Captain, the cult representatives have waited patiently for many watches to have an audience with you. Will you receive them, or do you wish to send them on their way without granting their request?"

traits.locale_text: “舰长大人，教派的众多代表已经耐心等待了几十巡，诚信希望能见您一面。您打算接待他们吗？还是说，您不打算答应他们的请求，希望打发他们回去？”

languages.text: 「ロード・キャプテン、教団の代表が、あなたとの謁見をずっと待っています。謁見しますか？それとも、彼らの要求を一切受け入れずに、帰らせますか？」
languages.original_text: "Lord Captain, the cult representatives have waited patiently for many watches to have an audience with you. Will you receive them, or do you wish to send them on their way without granting their request?"

traits.locale_text: 「ロード・キャプテン、教団の代表が、あなたとの謁見をずっと待っています。謁見しますか？それとも、彼らの要求を一切受け入れずに、帰らせますか？」

languages.text: "Lord Captain, die Vertreter des Kultes warten schon seit vielen Wachen geduldig auf eine Audienz mit Euch. Empfangt Ihr sie oder wollt Ihr sie wegschicken, ohne ihrer Bitte zu entsprechen?"
languages.original_text: "Lord Captain, the cult representatives have waited patiently for many watches to have an audience with you. Will you receive them, or do you wish to send them on their way without granting their request?"

languages.text: "Lord Kaptan, tarikat temsilcileri sizinle görüşmek için kaç vardiyadır sabırla bekliyor. Onları karşılayacak mısınız yoksa taleplerini yerine getirmeden göndermeyi mi dilersiniz?"
